snippet.title: MATTER Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a mystic and expressive world in a dynamic first person plateformer. Dive in a dreamlike and abstract world where matter evolves and lives around you according to your actions.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/978250/Matter/
Itch.io: https://uki-uki-lab.itch.io/matter
Website: https://sites.google.com/view/matterthegame/matter

■ Credits

Game Design, Programming, Support & Publishing by
    @MatoLabu

Music, Sound & Tech Art by
    @Tomavatars member of Concrete Games

2D & 3D Graphics by
    Monf

Game Design, Level Building, VFX & Programming by
    Paul Vaillé

Release: Publishing & Community Management by
    Le Mauvais Joueur

■ Uki Uki Lab

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/curator/44839609
